    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you make it a bit more intense? Like, I want him to sound more convinced that their way of life is actually dangerous or chaotic, and that they wouldn't even know what to do with \"civilization\" if it were given to them. Maybe add some more specific descriptions of how they live compared to how a \"proper\" society functions.",
